Maintainer: ArcheBase <noreply@archebase.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (=13),
               cmake

Package: axon-dispatcher
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         axon-recorder,
         axon-config,
         axon-panel,
         axon-transfer
Description: Axon Unified CLI Dispatcher
 Provides the 'axon' command that dispatches to subcommands
 like 'axon recorder', 'axon config', 'axon register', etc. (similar to git).
 .
 This creates a unified entry point for all Axon tools.
 .
 Recommend installing axon-all for a complete setup.
